To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AverageTrueRange _atr;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_atr = ATR(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_atr.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "truerange", _atr.TrueRange.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "averagetruerange", _atr.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.atr = self.ATR(symbol, period)

# In OnData()
if self.atr.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "truerange", self.atr.TrueRange.Current.Value)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "averagetruerange", self.atr.Current.Value)
